{"tid":1632533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人肯放低潔癖，團結起黎未?","createTime":"2019-10-06T18:24:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T05:36:03.000Z","uid":98079,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"694070f86feca1217b25992ad1c94aec5656fe87","tid":1632533,"uid":98079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:24:24.000Z","msg":"潔癖，香港依然好多人有潔癖<br />\n打人係唔啱架。放火係唔啱架<br />\n不如你話我聽點做先啱，點樣先係有效?<br />\n<br />\n點解警察到而家都未分化<br />\n警察每日都會提點住對方<br />\n保護好自己，保護屋企人，保護同袍<br />\n唔可以落單，唔可以離間，唔可以分化<br />\n要互相支持，要互相信任，要互相保護<br />\n最重要，大家安全收工<br />\n<br />\n所以，香港人<br />\n你願意放低你嘅潔癖未?<br />\n對方都團結，你又願意做到團結未?<br />\n做法唔完美，可改善<br />\n不分化，不割蓆<br />\n<br />\nps. 睇完呢篇嘅後感<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ThingsAtHongKong/photos/a.169826039860505/1323837631126001/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FThingsAtHongKong%2Fphotos%2Fa.169826039860505%2F1323837631126001%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEphyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=26965b23\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ThingsAtHongKong/photos/a.169826039860505/1323837631126001/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"834ebf1defd14ace558713dd7ceea629fb562634","tid":1632533,"uid":98079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:33:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a27e15b7c5a7450b328384a013ec05073997656","tid":1632533,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:34:06.000Z","msg":"岩 ！"},{"pid":"6190b78a775ad6514b17f97c96534a524dbadd4a","tid":1632533,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:34:49.000Z","msg":"可唔可以等埋人權法先呢?"},{"pid":"d8ac9ca6930fa2f385fd761070d2b818a8e27927","tid":1632533,"uid":311942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6190b78a775ad6514b17f97c96534a524dbadd4a","tid":1632533,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:34:49.000Z","msg":"可唔可以等埋人權法先呢?"},"citedBy