e6b7d8","tid":1632533,"uid":172345,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:48:53.000Z","msg":"其實唔係潔癖<br />\n係驚所謂暴力搞到我地輸<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只有一樣嘢可以令我地大步檻過<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632386\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632386</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:16:52.000Z","msg":"做法唔完美，可改善嘛<br />\n唔希望香港人第一句就屌左先<br />\n有啲藍絲都會睇前因後果先屌，點解我地嘅人唔睇左前因了解點解私了點解裝修先呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7079d7f47a10cf64aca82f428ab195b2e868e8ef","tid":1632533,"uid":63511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:17:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a9cb81bd8d2d17955312197d8d883465f129268","tid":1632533,"uid":90421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:18:25.000Z","msg":"和勇一齊食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不分和勇，入左黎先，攞番國際輿論又唔駛不反對通知書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632602-\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632602-</a> 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"331a5b3c9c09ac22a1be857560cfef665249c549","tid":1632533,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:19:14.000Z","msg":"［分化收皮］香港01分化民陣失敗，聲稱裝修過火、民意逆轉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632454\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632454</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f2657aac9fd969b9ac31d7f737b8eda720e76fb8","tid":1632533,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:20:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">今晚既連登超多兩極分化, 充滿負能量, 玩住TWITTER先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【3分鐘懶人包】依家整埋bot 教你玩 twitter, 連翻譯<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1594532\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1594532</a><br />\n<br />\n進階<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"de790f5e8ec598263cd2ebf77c915544d720fb01","ti